80.5	Ted_Kaczynski	Ted Kaczynski	Theodore John "Ted" Kaczynski , also known as the "Unabomber" (a portmanteau of university and airline bomber), is an American mathematician, social critic, anarcho-primitivist, and Neo-Luddite who engaged in a mail bombing campaign that spanned nearly 20 years, killing three people and injuring 23 others.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/37/Theodore_Kaczynski.jpg/220px-Theodore_Kaczynski.jpg
